    • FAQs

      Questions you may have, answered with
      • What are the key features of Samsung printers?
        Samsung printers often feature high-resolution printing, wireless connectivity, and eco-friendly settings. Some models include NFC and mobile print capabilities, duplex printing for two-sided documents, and high-yield toner options. Consider which features align with your printing needs, such as frequent color printing or primarily text documents.
        How'd we do?

      • What connectivity options are available?
        Samsung printers offer various connectivity options including USB, Ethernet, Wi-Fi, and sometimes Bluetooth. Wi-Fi-enabled printers support remote printing through apps like Samsung Mobile Print. Consider your setup to determine if you need a printer that supports wired or wireless connections, or both.
        How'd we do?
        Leave feedback about your eBay search experience - opens in new window or tabLeave feedback about your eBay search experience - opens in new window or tab
      • Are there eco-friendly features?
        Many Samsung printers include eco-friendly features such as Energy Star certification, automatic duplex printing to save paper, and toner-saving modes. These features not only help reduce environmental impact but can also lower operating costs over the printer's lifespan.
